=== 收视成绩 ===
《冰核计划》于1993年11月5日通过[[福斯广播公司|福克斯电视网]]在美国首播，1994年11月10日又经[[英国广播公司第二台|英国广播公司第二台]]在英国播映<ref name="dvdset">{{Cite AV media notes | title = The X-Files: The Complete First Season | year = 2004 | origyear = First broadcast 1993–1994 | others = Robert Mandel, Daniel Sackheim, et al. | type = booklet | publisher = Fox}}</ref>。节目在美国首播期间约有620万户家庭收看，观众人数约1000万<ref name="Lowry-1995" />{{rp|248}}<ref>{{cite news | title = Nielsen Ratings | accessdate = 2016-10-03 | newspaper = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | publisher = Gannett Company, Inc. | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = yes | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | url = http://anythingkiss.com/pi_feedback_challenge/Ratings/19930920-19931128_TVRatings.pdf | date = 1993-11-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053942/http://anythingkiss.com/pi_feedback_challenge/Ratings/19930920-19931128_TVRatings.pdf | page = D3 }}</ref>。[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森收视率]]数值为6.6，收视率11，意即当时所有装有电视的美国家庭中有6.6%收看本集，当时就在看电视的观众则有11%选择《冰核计划》<ref name="Lowry-1995" />{{rp|248}}。1996年，《冰核计划》和第一季第四集《[[奥卡布基湖奇案|奥卡布基湖奇案]]》（{{lang|en|''Conduit''}}）一起经{{lang|en|[[VHS|VHS]]}}录像带发行<ref>{{cite journal | date = 1997-01-11 | title = Video Sales | journal = [[告示牌_(杂志)|Billboard]] | volume = 109 | issue = 2 | page = 39 | issn = 0006-2510 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=wQ4EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PT38&lpg=PT38&dq=x+files+vhs+deep+throat&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=%22x%20files%22%20vhs%20deep%20throat&f=false | accessdate = 2016-10-06 | author = Nielsen Business Media Inc}}</ref>，还同第一季其他剧集一起收录到完整版{{lang|en|DVD}}中<ref name="dvdset" />。

=== 评价 ===
《冰核计划》播出后获得评论界赞誉。马特·赫尔维茨（{{lang|en|Matt Hurwitz}}）和克里斯·诺尔斯（{{lang|en|Chris Knowles}}）在合著的《完整{{lang|en|X}}档案》一书中指出，《{{lang|en|X}}档案》此时羽翼未丰，《冰核计划》相当于是节目的里程碑<ref>{{Cite book | title = The Complete X-Files | first1 = Matt | last1 = Hurwitz | first2 = Chris | last2 = Knowles | publisher = Insight Editions | year = 2008 | isbn = 1-933784-80-6 | page = 40}}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》在回顾第一季时给本集评分“{{lang|en|A}}−”（最高“{{lang|en|A}}+”），称赞节目气氛“特别紧张且节奏明快”<ref name="EW" />。基思·菲普斯（{{lang|en|Keith Phipps}}）在《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》撰文称赞本集表现，给予评级{{lang|en|A}}。在他看来，剧中演员完美演绎出角色的偏执，整集节目完全达到《{{lang|en|X}}档案》第一季的优异水准<ref name="AVC">{{cite web | url = http://www.avclub.com/tvclub/the-x-filesmillennium-ghost-in-the-machine-ice-spa-13061 | title = ''The X-Files'': "Ghost In The Machine" / "Ice" / "Space" | first = Keith | last = Phipps | work = [[影音俱乐部|The A.V. Club]] | date = 2008-07-05 | accessdate = 2016-10-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325152326/http://www.avclub.com/tvclub/the-x-filesmillennium-ghost-in-the-machine-ice-spa-13061 }}</ref>。《冰核计划》得以入选《影音俱乐部》的最伟大低成本单场景剧集之列，评论中称赞本集成功将封闭空间转变成节目的优势<ref name="avc2">{{cite web | url = http://www.avclub.com/article/tv-in-a-bottle-19-great-tv-episodes-largely-confin-42284 | title = TV in a bottle: 19 great TV episodes largely confined to one location | work = The A.V. Club | first1 = Jason | last1 = Heller | first2 = Genevieve | last2 = Koski | first3 = Noel | last3 = Murray | first4 = Sean | last4 = O'Neal | first5 = Leonard | last5 = Pierce | first6 = Scott | last6 = Tobias | first7 = Todd | last7 = VanDerWerff | first8 = Claire | last8 = Zulkey | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160320141004/http://www.avclub.com/article/tv-in-a-bottle-19-great-tv-episodes-largely-confin-42284 | date = 2010-06-21 | accessdate = 2016-10-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，该杂志还于2012年发文，把《冰核计划》列入《{{lang|en|X}}档案》的十大“必看”剧集，称正是这集首度证明，《{{lang|en|X}}档案》“的确有可能成为别具一格的节目”，文中还称赞本集“把幽闭恐惧症发挥得淋漓尽致”，而且成功展现出剧中英雄人物忐忑不安的心境和逐渐增强的信任<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160909090943/http://www.avclub.com/article/10-must-see-episodes-of-ithe-x-filesi-82714 | url = http://www.avclub.com/article/10-must-see-episodes-of-ithe-x-filesi-82714 | title = 10 must-see episodes of The X-Files | first = Todd | last = VanDerWerff | date = 2012-07-20 | accessdate = 2016-10-06 | work = The A.V. Club }}</ref>。

[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]网站的本·罗森-琼斯（{{lang|en|Ben Rawson-Jones}}）称，穆德和斯嘉丽在《冰核计划》中的对立气氛极度紧张，其中的偏执情绪达到极致<ref name="Digital">{{cite web | title = Classic Moment: Mulder vs Scully ('X-Files') | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201235107/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/news/a112344/classic-moment-mulder-vs-scully-x-files.html | url = http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-x-files/news/a112344/classic-moment-mulder-vs-scully-x-files/ | first1 = Ben | last1 = Rawson-Jones | date = 2008-07-20 | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | publisher = Hearst Magazines UK | work = Digital Spy | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》发文，称赞本集“卓具成效，而且令人毛骨悚然”，剧情足以同《[[阴阳魔界|阴阳魔界]]》相提并论<ref name="Lowry-1995" />{{rp|253}}。极客巢穴网站的马特·海格（{{lang|en|Matt Haigh}}）称本集“惊险且极具吸引力”，并在文中指出《冰核计划》和《怪形》的相似之处<ref name="Den">{{Cite web | date = 2008-10-28 | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | publisher = Den of Geek | url = http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/the-x-files/19691/revisiting-the-x-files-season-1-episode-8 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151101130213/http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/the-x-files/19691/revisiting-the-x-files-season-1-episode-8 | archivedate = 2015-11-01 | title = Revisiting The X-Files: Season 1 Episode 8 | first = Matt | last = Haigh }}</ref>，朱丽叶特·哈里森（{{lang|en|Juliette Harrisson}}）则认为本集是《{{lang|en|X}}档案》第一季中最优秀的独立剧情节目<ref>{{cite web |title=A look back over The X-Files’ finest stand-alone episodes |work=Den of Geek |publisher=Dennis Publishing |last=Harrisson |first=Juliette |date=2011-09-06 |archivedate=2016-03-25 |accessdate=2016-10-07 |url=http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/the-x-files/20936/a-look-back-over-the-x-files%E2%80%99-finest-stand-alone-episodes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325134730/http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/the-x-files/20936/a-look-back-over-the-x-files%E2%80%99-finest-stand-alone-episodes |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。电视小队的安娜·约翰斯（{{lang|en|Anna Johns}}）撰文赞扬本集表现堪称“壮观”，而且有“绝妙”的开场<ref name="TVS">{{cite web | url = http://www.aoltv.com/2006/07/23/the-x-files-ice/ | title = The X-Files: Ice | first = Anna | last = Johns | date = 2006-07-23 | accessdate = 2015-09-25 | work = TV Squad | publisher = [[赫芬顿邮报|Huffpost TV]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150926031644/http://www.aoltv.com/2006/07/23/the-x-files-ice/ | archivedate = 2015-09-26 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UGO}}网络称本集的蠕虫是《{{lang|en|X}}档案》中最出彩的“每周怪物”之一，让节目的刺激程度大幅增强<ref name="UGO">{{Cite web | url = http://www.ugo.com/movies/top-xfiles-monsters | archivedate = 2014-02-20 | title = Top 11 X-Files Monsters (of the Week) Intro | date = 2008-07-21 | accessdate = 2014-02-20 | work = UGO Networks | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140220094759/http://www.ugo.com/movies/top-xfiles-monsters | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Tor.com}}网站的梅根·迪恩斯（{{lang|en|Meghan Deans}}）把穆德和斯嘉丽在各自身上检查感染迹象的情节同《[[試播集_(X檔案)|試播集]]》（{{lang|en|''Pilot''}}）中的类似场景相比较，两个人都同样脆弱，只不过斯嘉丽在《冰核计划》中并不像《試播集》那样“像个白痴”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.tor.com/2011/11/10/reopening-the-x-files-ice/ | title = Reopening The X-Files: 'Ice' | first = Meghan | last = Deans | work = Tor.com | publisher = Tor Books | date = 2011-11-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330073958/http://www.tor.com/2011/11/10/reopening-the-x-files-ice/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-30 | accessdate = 2016-10-07 }}</ref>。[[罗伯特·谢尔曼|罗伯特·谢尔曼]]（{{lang|en|Robert Shearman}}）和[[拉斯·皮尔逊|拉斯·皮尔逊]]（{{lang|en|Lars Pearson}}）在著作《希望相信：{{lang|en|X}}档案批判指南，千禧年与孤胆枪手》（{{lang|en|''Wanting to Believe: A Critical Guide to The X-Files, Millennium & The Lone Gunmen''}}）中给予本星四星（最高五星）评价，称这是“有史以来最具影响的剧集”，并指出《{{lang|en|X}}档案》之后还多次采用同样的剧情格局。谢尔曼认为，虽然《冰核计划》的剧本衍生自其他作品，但摩根和黄毅瑜将《怪形》中的关键主题和完美的演员相结合，创造出至关重要的一集节目。<ref>{{cite book | year = 2009 | first1 = Robert | last1 = Shearman | first2 = Lars | last2 = Pearson | title = Wanting to Believe: A Critical Guide to The X-Files, Millennium & The Lone Gunmen | publisher = Mad Norwegian Press | isbn = 0-9759446-9-X | page = 16–17}}</ref>

《{{lang|en|X}}档案》剧组认为《冰核计划》是第一季最优秀的剧集之一。据卡特所言，摩根、黄毅瑜和导演[[戴维·纳特|戴维·纳特]]都在节目制作过程中超越自我，都在非常努力地工作。在他看来，《冰核计划》无论在剧本创作还是导演功底方面都发挥得淋漓尽致，而且一众配角演员表现同样出色。纳特对此表示：“《冰核计划》中最棒的地方在于，我们成功将那种强烈的偏执感传达出来。所有演员精诚合作，表现完美。我们在剧中处理的是每个角色最基本的情绪，从愤怒、无知再到恐惧，在两个一直相伴彼此的人物间建立情感纽带，这点非常重要。（此外，）把观众吓个半死无疑是这集的关键所在。”安德森也认为本集“非常紧张，充满恐惧和偏执，与我们合作的演员都很了不起。”<ref name="Edwards-1996" />{{rp|48–49}}

